Package edu.nyu.cs.javagit.client.cli

Interface Summary
IParser IParser is an interface for parsing a git command line output stream.
 

Class Summary
CliClient Command-line implementation of the IClient interface.
CliGitAdd Command-line implementation of the IGitAdd interface.
CliGitAdd.GitAddParser Parser class that implements IParser for implementing a parser for <git-add> output.
CliGitBranch Command-line implementation of the IGitBranch interface.
CliGitCheckout Command-line implementation of the IGitCheckout interface.
CliGitCheckout.GitCheckoutParser Parser class to parse the output generated by <git-checkout> and return a GitCheckoutResponse object.
CliGitCommit Command-line implementation of the IGitCommit interface.
CliGitDiff Command-line implementation of the IGitDiff interface.
CliGitGrep Command-line implementation of the IGitGrep interface.
CliGitLog Command-line implementation of the IGitLog interface.
CliGitMv Command-line implementation of the IGitMv interface.
CliGitReset Command-line implementation of the IGitReset interface.
CliGitRevert Command-line implementation of the IGitRevert interface.
CliGitRm Command-line implementation of the IGitRm interface.
CliGitShow Command-line implementation of the IGitShow interface.
CliGitStatus Command-line implementation of the IGitStatus interface.
CliGitStatus.GitStatusParser  
ProcessUtilities ProcessUtilities contains methods to help managing processes.
 

Enum Summary
CliGitStatus.Patterns Patterns for matching lines for deleted files, modified files, new files and empty lines.
